column5: Despite the dirty conditions there were still some steelhead to be found. Large robust Bunny jigs in Peach seemed to turn a few heads and fish too. Great weekend to be streamside.
Nice fish  Where can I get my hands on one of those....oh never mind
Good looking chrome for sure    Congratulations Leechman
Nice looking fish.  I've only ever used black and pink jigs.  Peach is a good idea.
